{
  "stem": "4710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I should look like the same, like the others.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when the SS man came and he saw me, he just picked me out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He just pulled me out and says, you go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You go to the other barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew what he want.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I started crying-- crying to him that I-- I'm strong.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I can work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was-- there was a German prisoner, that lageralteste, and he gave me a smack in the face and said, shut up, in German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the-- and the-- and the SS man said, ah, [INAUDIBLE] him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Leave him alone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So he pushed me back, and he took someone next to me, just like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was between life and death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And there was another selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That, I don't remember how I escaped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But by that-- by that time, I had experience how to always make myself-- whenever there is-- there is-- Mengele came into the camp, I just-- one thing one thing you have to know, that-- that when they make the selection, then-- then you don't-- you don't count the numbers that-- numbers that everybody is there.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if you are hiding, and you don't appear at the selection, then you can avoid it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I learned by the third selection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I survived all the three selections.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And do you think that because of your age and-- and size, you would have otherwise?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Inevitably--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would-- I-- yeah, no doubt about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No doubt about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would not-- in their eyes, I was not fit to work-- 14-year-old small, little boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it's not an-- not an asset for the German war machine, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
